# The live event log IS the registry - committed, so the repo is the log's
# permanent public home and `razor cite` log hashes are checkable by anyone
# with a checkout. Signing keys never leave the machine that made them.
# (demo.sh overwrites the log with fictional data locally; `git checkout
# registry/data/events.jsonl` restores the live one.)
registry/data/keys/
# Local contribution drafts from `razor upstream` - they leave via PRs, not commits here.
